sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Supplier
    participant App as TopKap App
    participant Bot as TopKap Bot
    participant API as Kayisoft API

    User->>App: Clicks "Connect Telegram"
    App->>API: Request Deep Link Token
    API-->>App: Returns JWT Token (15m expiry)
    App->>User: Opens tg://resolve?domain=TopKapTR_bot&start=TOKEN
    User->>Bot: Clicks Start (sends /start TOKEN)
    Bot->>API: POST /api/seller/telegram-bot/connect
    Note over Bot,API: Headers: Telegram-User-Id, Authorization, Platform, Accept-Language
    API-->>Bot: 200 OK (Success)
    Bot->>User: Shows Success Message & Main Menu

    User->>Channel: Adds Bot as Admin
    Channel->>Bot: my_chat_member event triggered
    Bot->>API: POST /api/seller/telegram-bot/create-channel
    API-->>Bot: 200 OK (Channel Registered)
    Bot->>User: Shows Channel Connected Message
